FBIS4-24586 "drchi105_d_94002" FBIS-CHI-94-105 Daily Report 31 May 1994 Northeast Asia Japanese Stock Firm First To Open Agency in Shandong Japanese Stock Firm First To Open Agency in Shandong SK0106040994 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network in Mandarin 2300 GMT 31 May 94 SK0106040994 Jinan Shandong People's Radio Network Mandarin BFN [Text] On the morning of 31 May, at Qilu Guesthouse, Wang Yuxi, vice governor of Shandong Province, cordially met with Mr. (Sokushima), deputy manager of (Hiyoshi) Stock Company in Japan. This is the first foreign financial and stock company to set up a representative agency in Shandong Province.
